Crimson Fungus=Škrlatna gliva
Crimson fungus is a mushroom found in the nether's crimson forest.=Škrlatna gliva je goba, ki jo najdemo v škrlatnem gozdu v Netherju.
Crimson Roots=Škrlatne korenine
Crimson Hyphae=Škrlatne hife
