Crimson Door=Škrlatna vrata

Wooden doors are 2-block high barriers which can be opened or closed by hand and by a redstone signal.=Lesena vrata so 2 bloka visoke pregrade, ki jih je mogoče odpreti ali zapreti z roko ali s signalom rdečega kamna.

To open or close a wooden door, rightclick it or supply its lower half with a redstone signal.=Za odpiranje ali zapiranje lesenih vrat desno kliknite nanje ali dovedite signal rdečega kamna v njihovo spodnjo polovico.

Crimson Trapdoor=Škrlatna loputa

Wooden trapdoors are horizontal barriers which can be opened and closed by hand or a redstone signal. They occupy the upper or lower part of a block, depending on how they have been placed. When open, they can be climbed like a ladder.=Lesene lopute so vodoravne pregrade, ki jih je mogoče odpreti in zapreti z roko ali s signalom rdečega kamna. Zasedajo zgornji ali spodnji del bloka, odvisno od tega, kako so bile postavljene. Ko so odprte, se po njih da plezati kot po lestvi.

To open or close the trapdoor, rightclick it or send a redstone signal to it.=Za odpiranje ali zapiranje lopute desno kliknite nanjo ali ji pošljite signal rdečega kamna.
Crimson Fence=Škrlatna ograja
Crimson Fence Gate=Škrlatna vrata ograje
